_ZN4llvm6AMDGPU9isComputeEj == llvm::AMDGPU::isCompute(unsigned int)
This looks like it is in lib/Target/AMDGPU/Utils.
So, looks like you need to build a amdgpu_utils library, like aarch64_utils. Then, add it as a dependency on the required libraries.
